# Now all about the stash 
-> Stash is a temparary storage like stack.

# When use a stash?
-> Stach will use when you write somthing but you don't want to commit right
-> So stash will move data into temporrary storage so 
-> Without interfier user work both branch


# How to use stach with cmds?
-> git stash          :- move into stash 
-> git stash list     :- Show the existing list
-> git stash apply    :- All stash back into orignal place
-> git stash apply@{0}:- Apply stash for some specific stash
-> git stash pop      :- Delete all the stash and apply all the stash